        <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
            <p>Jerome C. Knowlton joined the faculty as a full-time professor in 1886/87. He served as Dean of the Law School, 1891-1895, and returned to the faculty until is death in 1916.</p>
        </bioghist>



        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
            <p>The Knowlton collection consists of autographs and sentiments of University of Michigan faculty and photographs of Knowlton in classroom and with family members and a childhood
                photograph of Knowlton's daughter.</p>
        </scopecontent>

